                                                 throws java.lang.Exception
        For the given groupId and accountId, the function will return specific roles based on business validation. 1. For Nurse, only Patient Role will be returned. 2. For Support Member, no roles will be returned. 3. For Patient, only Nurse and Support Member role will be returned.
